headline: InvenTrust Properties: I'm Loading Up My Shopping Cart
summary: IVT's high-quality Sunbelt portfolio, essential retail, ultra-low debt, skilled management team, and emphasis on growing cash flows make it highly compelling. Read more about the REIT here.
